CFB: Injury Bug Hits Iowa City 
Updated: Tue, Oct 13 2015, 09:16 PM 
When the Hawkeyes travel to Northwestern Saturday, they'll be without Drew Ott. They'll be without Tevaun Smith. And who knows what their offensive line will look like. But as Mia O'Brien explains, when the injury bug bites... it's next man-up at Iowa. Related Stories   Ed Thomas Coach of the Week Faith, Family, Football.
